    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Robert Houdart</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/schaakfabriek/7074883983/in/set-72157629445845002/lightbox/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fc/RobertHoudart.jpg/300px-RobertHoudart.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/f/fc/RobertHoudart.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:RobertHoudart.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Robert Houdart <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Robert Houdart</b>,<br />\na Belgian computer scientist, professional software developer, amateur astronomer <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> , former chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, and author of the chess engine <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a>, which appeared in 2010 as closed source engine, free for non-commercial use, and leading the <a href=\"/IPON\" title=\"IPON\">IPON</a> <a href=\"/Engine_Rating_Lists\" title=\"Engine Rating Lists\">rating list</a> by <a href=\"/Ingo_Bauer\" title=\"Ingo Bauer\">Ingo Bauer</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> (January, 2011). In October 2011 with the release of Houdini 2, Robert Houdart has become professional chess programmer <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Houdart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Houdart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=342029&amp;t=33762\">Re: Visual C++ 2008 - good compiler/ linker settings for speed?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 13, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=10&amp;t=34333\">Introducing Houdini, a new, strong UCI chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 16, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=354023&amp;t=34673\">Re: question on draw evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 07, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Draw_Evaluation\" title=\"Draw Evaluation\">Draw Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35453\">Houdini 1.03 is available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=361912&amp;t=35338\">Re: Mate in 17 revisited</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 16, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Zugzwang\" title=\"Zugzwang\">Zugzwang</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35469\">Houdini 1.03a bug-fix is available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 17, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=368026&amp;t=35858\">Re: Plain and fancy magic on modern hardware</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 26, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37091\">Houdini 1.5 is released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 15, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40245\">Houdini 2 is released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40673\">Houdini 2 Aquarium released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 09, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=1647\">Computer Chess Biggest Liar</a> by <a href=\"/Franklin_Titus\" title=\"Franklin Titus\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, October 09, 2011 <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=436153&amp;t=41313\">Re: Any plans for Houdini 3?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 03, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=436467&amp;t=41272\">Re: Komodo 4 on long time control</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 04, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a>, <a href=\"/Strelka\" title=\"Strelka\">Strelka</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50304\">IPON results for Houdini 4</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 02, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/IPON\" title=\"IPON\">IPON</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Houdart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62035\">Houdini 5 has been released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 09, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65211\">Houdini 6 has been released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 18, 2017</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Houdart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cruxis.com/index.htm\">Cruxis Telescope Construction</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cruxis.com/chess/houdini.htm\">Houdini Chess Engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.365chess.com/players/Robert_Houdart\">Robert Houdart chess games - 365Chess.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chess-king.com/images/kingintromaterials/HoudartInterview/InterviewHoudiniA.pdf\">Interview of Robert Houdart, the Creator of the Strongest Chess Engine in the world: Houdini</a> (pdf), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chess-king.com/\">chess-king.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.chessbase.com/post/houdini-3-the-world-s-strongest-che-engine-in-the-fritz-interface\">Houdini 3 – the world's strongest chess engine in the Fritz interface - Interview with Robert Houdart, author of Houdini</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase News</a>, October 29, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vg.no/sport/i/49e9q/han-har-laget-sjakk-computeren-carlsen-ikke-toer-moete\">Han har laget sjakk-computeren Carlsen ikke tør møte - VG Nett om Sjakk</a>, November 20, 2013 (Norwegian) <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessdom.com/robert-houdart-on-houdini-5-dev-in-tcec/\">Robert Houdart on Houdini 5 dev in TCEC</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessdom&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chessdom (page does not exist)\">Chessdom</a>, August 25, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_9\" title=\"TCEC Season 9\">TCEC Season 9</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessdom.com/interview-with-robert-houdart-mark-lefler-and-gm-larry-kaufman/\">Interview with Robert Houdart, Mark Lefler and GM Larry Kaufman</a> by <a href=\"/Nelson_Hernandez\" title=\"Nelson Hernandez\">Nelson Hernandez</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessdom&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chessdom (page does not exist)\">Chessdom</a>, November 23, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_10\" title=\"TCEC Season 10\">TCEC Season 10</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessdom.com/interview-with-robert-houdart-author-of-the-champion-engine-houdini/\">Interview with Robert Houdart, author of the champion engine Houdini</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessdom&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chessdom (page does not exist)\">Chessdom</a>, December 08, 2017</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Houdart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/schaakfabriek/7074883983/in/set-72157629445845002/lightbox/\">Houdini: Flickr Album</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=207560\">Jan Lagrain</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://schaakfabriek.be/\">Schaakfabriek.be</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cruxis.com/scope/scope1100.htm\">Design and Construction of the 110 cm Cruxis Telescope</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.365chess.com/players/Robert_Houdart\">Robert Houdart chess games - 365Chess.com</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.inwoba.de/index.html\">IPON-Rating-List</a> by <a href=\"/Ingo_Bauer\" title=\"Ingo Bauer\">Ingo Bauer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40245\">Houdini 2 is released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2011</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40728\">Houdini with 1:1 Robbolito-code?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dr._Alexander_Schmidt&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dr. Alexander Schmidt (page does not exist)\">Dr. Alexander Schmidt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 2011</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=428534&amp;t=40728\">Re: Houdini with 1:1 Robbolito-code?</a> by <a href=\"/Norman_Schmidt\" title=\"Norman Schmidt\">Norman Schmidt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 2011</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.chessbase.com/post/carlsen-wuerde-mit-2-8-verlieren\">\"Carlsen würde mit 2:8 verlieren\"</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase.de</a>, November 20, 2013 (German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magnus_Carlsen\">Magnus Carlsen from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Chess_Championship_2013\">World Chess Championship 2013 - Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301154220\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.024 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.026 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 163/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 362/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4703-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301154220 and revision id 8723\n -->\n"
